data.description: **CHECK OUT RECENT PRICE CHANGE**Welcome to your dream home with no HOA! This warm and inviting haven is perfect for family gatherings during the holidays, moments of fellowship, or watching the big game by the cozy gas log fireplace. Hardwood floors and elegant moldings grace the formal living room and dining room, creating an atmosphere of timeless charm. Step outside onto the massive patio, an idyllic retreat to sip your favorite beverage and unwind. The formal dining room, spacious enough for all your guests, sets the scene for memorable dinners. The colossal owners suite boasts a posh private bath, providing a serene sanctuary. The upscale kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring granite counters and ready for crafting all your family's favorite recipes. Enjoy the convenience of under-cabinet lighting, adding a touch of sophistication to your culinary endeavors. Enjoy the spacious 4 bedrooms, including the huge owners suite, providing ample space for the entire family. All the formals add a touch of elegance, while the loft offers additional room for relaxation or recreation. Situated on a corner lot, this property offers both space and privacy. Noteworthy upgrades include a recent replacement of the roof and HVAC systems, ensuring both comfort and durability for years to come. This property is more than a home; it's a canvas for cherished memories. Make it yours today! Contact us for a private viewing.
